ref="https://www.nme.com/news/music/halsey-reveals-shes-lucky-to-be-alive-after-health-struggles-as-she-shares-new-single-the-end-3762516">The End》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-halseys-emotive-nine-inch-nails-inspired-new-single-lonely-is-the-muse-3784426">《Lonely Is The Muse》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/halsey-was-really-nervous-about-clearing-britney-spears-lucky-sample-shared-everything-with-her-before-release-3780469">《Lucky》</a> ，定于 10 月 25 日发行，<a href="https://www.halseymusicstore.eu/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">现已开放预购</a>。 《伟大的模仿者》将作为 2021 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/halsey-if-i-cant-have-love-i-want-power-review-3030014">《如果我不能拥有爱，我想要力量》</a>的后续作品，也是哈尔西的第五张录音室专辑。</p><p>在对 2021 年唱片的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/halsey-if-i-cant-have-love-i-want-power-review-3030014">四星评价</a>中， <em>NME</em>分享道：“几乎不用说，这张专辑非常激烈，而且并不完全充满轻松的轻松感。这也是只有哈尔西才能做出的错综复杂、无穷无尽的令人信服的艺术宣言。”</p><p>哈尔西此后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/halsey-says-new-album-is-all-over-the-place-and-full-of-experimentation-3776430">开玩笑说她的新唱片将“无处不在”并且“充满实验”。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/halsey-reveals-she-was-hospitalised-after-suffering-very-scary-seizure-3797446">哈尔西透露她在遭受“非常可怕”的癫痫发作后住院治疗的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
 U2分享“如何拆除原子弹”环节中的新歌“Country Mile”和“Picture Of You (X + W)” https://www.nme.com/news/music/u2-share-new-songs-country-mile-and-picture-of-you-xw-from-how-to-dismantle-an-atomic-bomb- sessions-3797417?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=u2-share-new-songs-country-mile-and-picture-of-you-xw-from-how-to-dismantle-an-atomic-bomb-sessionsHollie Geraghty Thu, 26 Sep 2024 16:00:16 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3797417 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/u2-how-to-dismantle-atomic-bomb-anniversary.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="U2" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/u2-how-to-dismantle-atomic-bomb-anniversary.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/u2-how-to-dismantle-atomic-bomb-anniversary-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/u2-how-to-dismantle-atomic-bomb-anniversary-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/u2-how-to-dismantle-atomic-bomb-anniversary-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/u2-how-to-dismantle-atomic-bomb-anniversary-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/u2-how-to-dismantle-atomic-bomb-anniversary-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这些新曲目收录在这支爱尔兰摇滚乐队即将发行的“影子专辑”中，以纪念他们 2004 年格莱美获奖唱片 20 周年，其中将收录 10 首“未发行的宝石”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/u2-share-new-songs-country-mile-and-picture-of-you-x-w-from-how-to-dismantle-an-atomic-bomb-sessions-3797417">U2 分享的新歌《How To Dismantle An Atomic Bomb》中的《Country Mile》和《Picture Of You (X + W)》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/u2-how-to-dismantle-atomic-bomb-anniversary.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="U2" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/u2-how-to-dismantle-atomic-bomb-anniversary.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/u2-how-to-dismantle-atomic-bomb-anniversary-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/u2-how-to-dismantle-atomic-bomb-anniversary-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/u2-how-to-dismantle-atomic-bomb-anniversary-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/u2-how-to-dismantle-atomic-bomb-anniversary-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/u2-how-to-dismantle-atomic-bomb-anniversary-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/u2">U2</a>分享了两首新歌，名为“Country Mile”和“Picture Of You (X + W)”，取自他们“How To Dismantle An Atomic Bomb”的原始曲目 - 请在下面聆听。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/u2-las-vegas-sphere-setlist-photos-3506848">U2 拉斯维加斯现场演出：在价值 20 亿美元的 Sphere 上呈现令人眼花缭乱的首演之夜</a></strong></li></ul><p>为了庆祝他们标志性的第 11 张录音室专辑，这支爱尔兰摇滚乐队宣布发行一张名为“如何重新组装原子弹”的影子专辑。</p><p>即将发行的唱片（<a href="https://u2.lnk.to/HTDAAB20" target="_blank" rel="noopener">可在此处预订</a>）将包括从原始专辑的存档中挖掘出来的未发行的新歌曲。</p><p>与新项目一起，《如何拆除原子弹》首次被重新制作为 20 周年特别版，其中包括附赠曲目《Fast Cars》。</p><p> “重新组装版”——包含“如何拆除原子弹”和“如何重新组装原子弹”将于 11 月 22 日以双数字版本形式提供。</p><p>新项目的前两个试用版现已推出，您可以在下面查看更多发布详细信息。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="U2 - Country Mile [官方歌词视频]" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/KVW-xthPZSE?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="U2 - Picture of You (X+W) [官方歌词视频]" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/_fIXQXTE-v8?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>重制版《如何拆除原子弹》也将于 11 月 22 日以实体形式发行，您可以<a href="https://atomicbomb.u2.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>探索。与此同时，《How To Re-Assemble An Atomic Bomb》将在黑色星期五唱片店日以限量版黑色和红色大理石 1LP 黑胶唱片形式独家发售，并于 11 月 29 日以独立的 10 首曲目数字版本发售。</p><p>乐队从专辑录制时代挑选了10首“未发行的宝石”与歌迷分享。在关于新专辑周年纪念版的新闻声明中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-edge">The Edge</a>分享道：“《如何拆除原子弹》的会议对乐队来说是一个充满创意的时期，我们在录音室里探索了很多歌曲创意。我们受到启发，重新审视我们早期的音乐影响，对于<a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bono">波诺</a>来说，这是一个深刻的个人反省的时期，他试图处理——拆除——他父亲的死亡。</p><p> “对于这个周年纪念版，我进入了我的个人档案，看看是否有任何未发布的宝石，我中了大奖。我们选择了十个真正适合我们的。尽管当时我们把这些歌曲放在一边，但事后看来，我们认识到我们最初对它们成为专辑竞争者的直觉是正确的，我们做了一些事情。</p><p>吉他手总结道：“你在这张影子专辑中得到的是发现的原始能量、音乐的发自内心的影响、声音叙事、时间的某个时刻、四位音乐家在一个房间里一起演奏的探索和互动……这是纯粹的 U2 掉落物。” </p><figure id="attachment_3797423" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3797423" style="width: 3000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3797423" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/u2-how-to-dismantle-an-atomic-bomb-reissue.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="3000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/u2-how-to-dismantle-an-atomic-bomb-reissue.jpg 3000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/u2-how-to-dismantle-an-atomic-bomb-reissue-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/u2-how-to-dismantle-an-atomic-bomb-reissue-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/u2-how-to-dismantle-an-atomic-bomb-reissue-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/u2-how-to-dismantle-an-atomic-bomb-reissue-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/u2-how-to-dismantle-an-atomic-bomb-reissue-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/202